    <item>
      <title>丘吉尔的施维默表示私人信贷收益率将在较长时间内维持高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/churchill-s-schwimmer-sees-private-credit-yields-high-for-longer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丘吉尔资产管理公司副董事长兰迪施维默表示，利率将在较长时间内维持在高位，从而为私人债务投资者带来收益提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/churchill-s-schwimmer-sees-private-credit-yields-high-for-longer</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 14:34:59 GMT</pubDate>
